rows.label: qev030503_MSG0001
rows.name: I miss you, Quegga. I want you to hold me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030503_MSG0003
rows.name:
You are BLADE, yes? I ask nothing of you.
World without Quegga can give me nothing.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030503_MSG0004
rows.name:
I used to dance all night. I wore beautiful clothes
that Quegga made for me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030503_MSG0005
rows.name:
I danced to make him happy, but he is gone.
Now dancing means nothing.[ST:wait ]
